  "instructions": [
    "Prepare the kimchi by slicing it into thin strips and setting it aside.",
    "In a large bowl, combine the sliced cucumber, grated carrots, and sliced zucchini.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the sesame oil, soy sauce, and minced garlic to make the dressing.",
    "Pour the dressing over the vegetables and toss to coat.",
    "Add the cooked rice to the bowl and stir to combine with the vegetables and dressing.",
    "Add the kimchi to the bowl and stir gently to combine.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a cataplana vessel and top with chopped green onions and toasted sesame seeds.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
